import React from "react"
interface Props{
    handleButtonClick: ()=>void,
    size:string,
}

const AddButton : React.FC<Props> = ({ handleButtonClick,size }) => {
  return (
    <>
      <svg
        className='addBtn'
        onClick={handleButtonClick}
        width={size}        height={size}
        viewBox='0 0 45 45'
        fill='none'
        xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'
      >
        <path
          d='M22.5 15.625V22.5M22.5 22.5V29.375M22.5 22.5H29.375M22.5 22.5H15.625M43.125 22.5C43.125 33.8909 33.8909 43.125 22.5 43.125C11.1091 43.125 1.875 33.8909 1.875 22.5C1.875 11.1091 11.1091 1.875 22.5 1.875C33.8909 1.875 43.125 11.1091 43.125 22.5Z'
          stroke='#545F71'
          stroke-width='2'
          stroke-linecap='round'
          stroke-linejoin='round'
        />
      </svg>
    </>
  )
}
export default AddButton
